('200003003009','Volume formed when R is rotated about the x-axis:;$$\\begin{align};  & V=\\int_{1}^{3}{\\pi {{y}^{2}}dx} \\\\ ; & =\\pi \\int_{1}^{3}{{{\\left[ {{\\left( {{x}^{3}}+1 \\right)}^{\\frac{1}{4}}} \\right]}^{2}}dx}=\\pi \\int_{1}^{3}{{{\\left( {{x}^{3}}+1 \\right)}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}dx} \\\\ ;\\end{align}$$;;Let $$y=f\\left( x \\right)=\\left( {{x}^{3}}+1 \\right)\\frac{1}{4}$$;Trapezium rule:;$$\\int\\limits_{a}^{b}{ydx}\\approx \\frac{1}{2}h\\left[ {{y}_{0}}+{{y}_{n}}+2\\left( {{y}_{1}}+{{y}_{2}}+...+{{y}_{n-1}} \\right) \\right]$$;where h = width of each trapezium, and yi is the value of y at x = a+ih.;With b = 3, a = 1 and n = 4 and $$h=\\frac{b-a}{n}=\\frac{3-1}{4}=0.5$$;\\[\\begin{align};  & {{y}_{0}}={{\\left[ {{\\left( 1.0 \\right)}^{3}}+1 \\right]}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}=1.4142 \\\\ ; & {{y}_{1}}={{\\left[ {{\\left( 1.5 \\right)}^{3}}+1 \\right]}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}=2.0916 \\\\ ; & {{y}_{2}}={{\\left[ {{\\left( 2.0 \\right)}^{3}}+1 \\right]}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}=3.0000 \\\\ ; & {{y}_{3}}={{\\left[ {{\\left( 2.5 \\right)}^{3}}+1 \\right]}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}=4.0773 \\\\ ; & {{y}_{4}}={{\\left[ {{\\left( 3.0 \\right)}^{3}}+1 \\right]}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}=5.2915 \\\\ ; &  \\\\ ; & \\therefore \\pi \\int_{1}^{3}{{{\\left( {{x}^{3}}+1 \\right)}^{\\frac{1}{2}}}dx} \\\\ ; & \\approx \\pi \\frac{1}{2}h\\left[ {{y}_{0}}+{{y}_{4}}+2\\left( {{y}_{1}}+{{y}_{2}}+{{y}_{3}} \\right) \\right] \\\\ ; & =\\pi \\frac{1}{2}\\left( 0.5 \\right)\\left[ 1.4142+5.2915+2\\left( 2.0916+3.0000+4.0773 \\right) \\right] \\\\ ; & =19.669=19.67 \\\\ ;\\end{align}\\];'),
