('20020400105', '200204001', 5, '(a)	The producer of a play requires a total cast of 5, of which 3 are actors and 2 are actresses. He auditions 5 actors and 4 actresses for the cast. Find the total number of ways in which the cast can be obtained.;(b)	Find how many different odd 4-digit numbers less than 4000 can be made from the digits 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7 if no digit may be repeated.', 55, 5501, 1, 'Exam Paper',0),
