(183,'Deriving_Partial_Fraction_From_Quadratic_Factor','F',40,'Partial Fraction - Case 3: Quadratic Factor which does not factorise e.g. $$\\frac{mx + n}{(ax + b)(x^2 + c^2)}$$, express in $$\\frac{A}{ax + b} + \\frac{Bx + C}{x^2 + c^2}$$'),
